headline: Three Reasons Why WDC is Risky and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the last six months, Western Digital’s shares have sunk to $71.51, producing a disappointing 7.6% loss - a stark contrast to the S&P 500’s 14.2% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
